# Community Building Resources
Bringing the Nodejs local community meetups together

### Interested in starting a Node event for your community, here are some ideas: 
1. [NodeSchool - series of workshops on javascript, node and more](https://github.com/nodeschool/organizers/wiki)
2. [NodeTodo - self-serve contributing to node](http://nodetodo.org/)
3. [Code & Learn - contributing to node with attendance of node ](https://nodejs.org/en/get-involved/code-and-learn/)
4. [Structure and Tips for successful Nodejs meetup](https://github.com/nodejs/evangelism/edit/master/documents/local_initiatives/README.md)

### Want to join existing meetups in your community, find them below:
